<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV88">
<l>tirumā luruvokkum mēruvam mēruviṟ ceñcuṭarōṉ</l>
<l>ṟirumāl tirukkait tiruccak karamokku maṉṉakaṇṭun</l>
<l>tirumā luruvō ṭavaṉciṉṉa mēpitaṟ ṟāniṟpatōr</l>
<l>tirumāl talaikkoṇṭa naṅkaṭkeṅ kēvarun tīviṉaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Although seeing mount Meru that equals the form of Tirumāl [and] the red sun</l>
<l>on that Meru as equal to the brilliant discus in Tirumāl’s holy hand</l>
<l>there is constant raving about the form of Tirumāl and his symbols.</l>
<l>To us who have taken possession of unique Tirumāl, whence will come evil deeds?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
